items.title: Bump typed-rest-client and azure-pipelines-tool-lib in /tasks/install

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

items.body:
Bumps [typed-rest-client](https://github.com/Microsoft/typed-rest-client) to 1.8.9 and updates ancestor dependency [azure-pipelines-tool-lib](https://github.com/microsoft/azure-pipelines-tool-lib). These dependencies need to be updated together. Updates `typed-rest-client` from 1.0.9 to 1.8.9
Release notes

Sourced from typed-rest-client's releases.

1.5.0

Enable webpack to be used on this library. Previously failed due to dynamic dependencies

1.4.0

Propogate headers in RestClient's IRestResponse Upgrade to TypeScript 3.5.1 Support presigned urls

Commits
  • See full diff in compare view
Maintainer changes

This version was pushed to npm by martinmrazik, a new releaser for typed-rest-client since your current version.


Updates `azure-pipelines-tool-lib` from 0.12.0 to 2.0.4
